{"content":"<div id=\"Ps.126\" class=\"chapter\">\n<h3 class=\"d\">上行之诗。</h3>\n<h3 class=\"s\">被掳归回者的欢乐</h3>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v1\"><sup id=\"Ps.126.1\" class=\"v1\">1</sup>当耶和华使<span class=\"pn\">锡安</span>被掳的人归回的时候，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v1\">我们好像做梦的人。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\"><sup id=\"Ps.126.2\" class=\"v2\">2</sup>那时，我们满口喜笑、</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">满舌欢呼；</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v2\">那时，列国中就有人说：</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v2\">“耶和华为他们行了大事！”</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v3\"><sup id=\"Ps.126.3\" class=\"v3\">3</sup>耶和华果然为我们行了大事，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v3\">我们就欢喜。</span></p>\n<p class=\"b\"></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v4\"><sup id=\"Ps.126.4\" class=\"v4\">4</sup>耶和华啊，求你使我们这些被掳的人归回，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v4\">好像<span class=\"pn\">尼革夫</span>的河水复流。</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v5\"><sup id=\"Ps.126.5\" class=\"v5\">5</sup>流泪撒种的，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v5\">必欢呼收割！</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v6\"><sup id=\"Ps.126.6\" class=\"v6\">6</sup>那带种流泪出去的，</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v6\">必欢呼地带禾捆回来！</span></p>\n</div>\n"}